NHP Glucose, Body Weight, and Body Comp

Eric Shiroma, John Nam

2020 April 07

Study Description

  • This is an investigation into the longitudinal trajectories of glucose, body weight, and body composition in NHP (non-human primate colonies). These results will be used to compare similar trajectories in mice and humans.

function to coalesce columns with missing values

study bounded to non-caloric restriction diet monkeys

    • monkeys on caloric restriction diet: 91
    • monkeys on control diet: 263

excluding monkeys with no valid metabolic index values
